    description: 'A young witch becomes a hollow vessel after losing her True Name,
      the anchor of her soul and power. Now a "nameless" entity invisible to spirits,
      she hunts through dark archives and bargains with demons to reclaim the word
      that defines her existence.

      Should we focus on the thief who stole her
      name, or the unpredictable side effects of her unanchored magic?'
